name: FrontEnd Chain
description: The vigorous development of front-end technology has brought it to a new level, which has also caused some problems. Such as component abuse, abandonment of maintenance, intellectual copyright, invalid solutions, and a series of problems. Front End Chain is committed to the development and research of front-end industry technology, and people or organizations that have contributed to the development of the front-end industry will make free donations in the form of FEC tokens.
